org.codehaus.janino

Interface Visitor.BlockStatementVisitor<R,EX extends java.lang.Throwable>

  • Type Parameters:
    R - The type of the object returned by the visit*() methods
    EX - The exception that the visit*() methods may throw
    Enclosing class:
    Visitor

    public static interface Visitor.BlockStatementVisitor<R,EX extends java.lang.Throwable>
    The visitor for all kinds of Java.BlockStatements (statements that may appear with a block).
